message:
Replaces system-dependent line separator by %n in printf

Signed-off-by: Manoel Campos <manoelcampos@gmail.com>

added: "%n# %.2f: Intentionally destroying %s due to CPU overload. Current VM CPU usage is %.2f%%%n",
datacenter0.getHostList().forEach(h -> System.out.printf("# %.2f: %s CPU Utilization %.2f%%%n", info.getTime(), h, h.getCpuPercentUtilization()*100));
deleted: "\n# %.2f: Intentionally destroying %s due to CPU overload. Current VM CPU usage is %.2f%%\n",
datacenter0.getHostList().forEach(h -> System.out.printf("# %.2f: %s CPU Utilization %.2f%%\n", info.getTime(), h, h.getCpuPercentUtilization()*100));
